---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — Age Calculator | Usage Guidelines"
  description="Terms of service for the Age Calculator. Informational tool only. No warranty. Results may vary slightly based on browser date handling."
  canonical="https://agecalculatordob.pages.dev/terms/"
  ogType="website"
>
  <div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 w-full bg-canvas/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-hairline shadow-level-1 min-h-14 md:min-h-16 transition-all" role="banner">
      <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-3 md:px-6 py-2 md:py-0 flex items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-1.5 focus-ring rounded-sm py-1 shrink-0" aria-label="Age Calculator — Home">
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] md:text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-mute">0.0.1</span>
          <span class="font-sans font-semibold text-sm md:text-lg tracking-tight select-none text-ink leading-tight">AGE CALCULATOR.</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/"
          class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-canvas hover:bg-canvas-soft-2 text-ink border border-hairline rounded-sm font-mono text-[10px] md:text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider focus-ring transition cursor-pointer"
          aria-label="Back to Age Calculator"
        >← Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="flex-1 w-full max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 py-12 md:py-20" role="main">
      <article class="prose prose-sm md:prose-base max-w-none">
        <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="mb-6">
          <ol class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs text-mute font-mono">
            <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-ink focus-ring rounded-sm">Home</a></li>
            <li aria-hidden="true">/</li>
            <li aria-current="page" class="text-ink font-semibold">Terms of Service</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>

        <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-ink tracking-tight mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-mute font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mb-8">Last updated: June 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-body text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Use of the Tool</h2>
            <p>The Age Calculator is provided as an informational tool only. It is designed to give you an approximate measure of time elapsed since a given birth date. While we strive for accuracy, you should not rely on this tool for legal, medical, or financial decisions.</p>
          </section>

          <section class="bg-canvas border border-hairline rounded-lg p-5 md:p-6 space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-mute shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-sm">01.</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-ink font-semibold block">Informational Purpose Only</strong>
                <span class="text-body text-sm">All calculations and statistics are for entertainment and informational purposes. They do not constitute professional advice.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-mute shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-sm">02.</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-ink font-semibold block">Results May Vary</strong>
                <span class="text-body text-sm">Age calculations depend on your browser's date and time handling, including timezone offsets and leap year rules. Slight variations (&lt; 1 day) may occur across different browsers or devices.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-mute shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-sm">03.</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-ink font-semibold block">No Warranty</strong>
                <span class="text-body text-sm">This tool is provided "as is" without any warranty, express or implied. The authors make no guarantees about accuracy, availability, or fitness for a particular purpose.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-mute shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-sm">04.</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-ink font-semibold block">User Responsibility</strong>
                <span class="text-body text-sm">You are solely responsible for how you use the information generated by this tool. We are not liable for any consequences arising from the use of this tool.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-mute shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-sm">05.</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-ink font-semibold block">Future Changes</strong>
                <span class="text-body text-sm">Features, design, and functionality may change in future releases without notice. We reserve the right to update or discontinue the tool at any time.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p>The design, code, and content of this tool are original work. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without prior permission.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Governing Law</h2>
            <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the jurisdiction in which the tool's authors reside. Any disputes shall be resolved in the appropriate local courts.</p>
          </section>

          <div class="pt-6 border-t border-hairline">
            <a href="/"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 bg-primary hover:bg-neutral-800 text-on-primary rounded-sm font-sans font-medium text-sm focus-ring transition shadow-level-2"
            >← Back to Age Calculator</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </div>
</Layout>
